                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">To the Editor of the Occident</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">The undersigned begs leave, to in,,<lb/>,,form his\n                                        Hebrew Bretheren, that at present he<lb/> is out of\n                                                  implac<add>?</add>, and wanted be willing to<lb/>\n                                        attend the Holy worship, in one of our<lb/>\n                                        <sic>Synagauges</sic>, in any place, of the <placeName>U.\n                                                  S.</placeName><lb/> in all its Branches,</p>\n                              <p><sic>Refrences</sic>, the <persName>Revd. J. J. Lyon's</persName>\n                                        <placeName>N. Y.</placeName></p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                                        <add>Hebrew</add>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">Isaac Moses Statky</persName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">care of <persName>Mr. E. Bernheimer</persName></p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">\n                                        <placeName>\n                                                  <hi rend=\"underline\">Buffalo. N. Y.</hi>\n                                        </placeName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p><placeName>Buffalo</placeName>, <date>Tamus 19. <hi\n                                                  rend=\"underline\">5608</hi></date></p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                                        <date>July 20. 1848</date>\n                              </p>"
